@Deprecated public static class ShadowTelecomManager.CallRecord extends Object
Deprecated.
Use ShadowTelecomManager.IncomingCallRecord or ShadowTelecomManager.UnknownCallRecord instead.
Details about a call request made via TelecomManager.addNewIncomingCall(android.telecom.PhoneAccountHandle, android.os.Bundle) or TelecomManager.addNewUnknownCall(android.telecom.PhoneAccountHandle, android.os.Bundle).
